ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P1: Gwiritsani ntchito kayendetsedwe ka ndalama kuti mupereke chithandizo chodalirika, chotheka, chofikira padziko lonse kuchipatala mkati mwa mphindi khumi kapena zochepera.
ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P2: MDS ya Saluber inakonzedwa kuti idzasinthire maubwenzi odwala ndi odwala mwa kulenga 24/7 kupeza chithandizo chamankhwala padziko lonse lapansi.
about_us_section1_p1: SaluberMD ndi bungwe la Digital Health lomwe linadzipereka kuti likhale lopereka thandizo la zachipatala ndi mankhwala kuti zipititse patsogolo zaumoyo padziko lonse lapansi. Dipatimenti Yathu Yogulitsa Mankhwala Opanga Zamalonda, amapereka mwayi wopindula ndi thanzi labwino, madokotala ovomerezedwa ndi bungwe, maofesi a zachipatala m'zinenero 18, zovala zoyenera kuti aziwunika thanzi lanu, ndi kupeza maukonde a ogwira ntchito zaumoyo ndi mautumiki.
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P1:
Kupyolera mu geo-kumalo athu pulogalamu yathu idzapeza bwino Dokotala pafupi nawe. Achipatala a SaluberMD akhoza kudziwa, kuchiza, kapena kukambirana za matenda anu kudzera mu kanema ndikukupatsani dongosolo loyenera la mankhwala. Zambiri zomwe zimachitika mu ofesi ya dokotala zimatha kuchiritsidwa ndi kuyendera mavidiyo.
Zina mwa zinthu zomwe timachita:
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P2: Mbiri Yanu Yamankhwala Ndi malo abwino oti musungire deta yanu yonse, zithunzi ndi mafayilo. Onetsetsani thanzi lanu ndi kupeza 24/7 kwa zolemba zanu zonse zachipatala. Kaya muli pakhomo kapena mukupita kunja, zomwe mukudziŵa ndizomwe mungathe kugawana ndi dokotala wanu. Kusavuta kugwiritsa ntchito zolemba zachipatala kumapezeka m'zinenero 18.
ABOUT_US_SECTION3_P1: Amayi okhawo omwe amadziwika bwino amapereka chithandizo chamankhwala pa SaluberMD. Ogwira ntchitowa akutsimikiziridwa, akuwonetsedwa kwambiri ndikuphunzitsidwa kuti apereke chisamaliro chapamwamba. Dokotala aliyense ali ndi bio komwe mungathe kuwona maziko, zidziwitso, ndi chidziwitso chawo. SaluberMD yadzipereka ku kasamalidwe kabwino ka azinthu athu. Ndondomeko yamakono imalola odwala kuyeza madokotala ndikuwona madokotala onse.

PRICING_SECTION1_P1: SaluberMD yadzipereka kupereka zabwino, zosamalira zamtengo wapatali pamtengo wotsika mtengo popanda malipiro kapena zobisika.
PRICING_SECTION1_P2: SaluberMD imapereka chisamaliro kulikonse ndi nthawi iliyonse yomwe muyifuna kudzera muvidiyo kuyendera dokotala wovomerezeka. Madokotala athu akhoza kukambirana, kufufuza, ndi kumvetsera kuti adziwe zomwe mukukumana nazo kapena kungoyankha mafunso azachipatala ndi zodetsa nkhaŵa panthawi ya pulogalamuyi.
PRICING_SECTION1_P3: Ndi Medicfile yathu yokhayo mungapereke dokotala wanu mwayi wofikira mbiri yanu ya zamankhwala, zithunzi zanu ndi mafayilo kuti awathandize kupanga njira yothandiza kwambiri ya mankhwala.

QUALITY_INDEX_DESCRIPTION: Kukhala ndi thupi labwino ndilo msinkhu wa kupirira ndi kupsinjika maganizo komwe kukukumana nako pakukwanitsa kusintha ndi kusamalira mkhalidwewo. Zizindikiro zakuthupi zimasonyeza thupi la munthu kuti ligwirizane ndi kusintha kwa chilengedwe ndi kukhumudwitsa, kusunga ndi kubwezeretsanso thanzi labwino. Kukhala wathanzi nthawi zambiri kumawonetseratu mwakukhoza kwa miyoyo ya anthu, kuphunzira, ndi ntchito, komanso mwachibadwa m'zochita zolimbitsa thupi. Ubwino wa umunthu wamunthu umagwirizana ndi chibadwidwe koma umagwirizana kwambiri ndi zakudya zomwe amapeza komanso zolimbitsa thupi. Kupyolera mu njira zoyenera ndi kuchita masewero olimbitsa thupi, iye akhoza kukulitsa thupi lake m'thupi lonse.
QUESTIONS_SECTION_TITLE: Landirani 1 kulankhulana kwaulere kapena kuyitanitsa zaumoyo mutatha kukwaniritsa fayilo lanu lachipatala.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P1: Ku SaluberMD timayesetsa kukwaniritsa zofuna za umoyo wabwino padziko lonse lapansi powapatsa makasitomala athu mwayi wopita ku gulu lodziwika bwino la asing'anga.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P2: Nthawi zonse timayang'ana madokotala kuti azitha kuwonjezera gulu lathu labwino. Monga membala wa timu yathu timalemekeza ndikuyamikira kutumiza kwanu.
RECOMMEND_SECTION_P3: Chonde lembani fomu ili m'munsiyi kuti mutumize Dokotala kwa SaluberMD

rr_desc: Mpweya wa kupuma ndi mlingo umene kupuma kumachitika. Kupuma kwabwino kwa munthu wamkulu pa kupuma ndiko mpweya wa 12 mpaka 20 pa mphindi. Kupuma kwapakati pa 12 kapena kupitirira 25 mpweya pa mphindi pamene kupumula kumaonedwa kuti sikunali kwachilendo
sai_desc: SAI imachokera pamtima wanu. Ndi mzere wosavuta womwe umayang'ana momwe thupi limayankhira pa zochitika zathupi - zambiri kuposa zongopeka chabe. Mosiyana ndi kutsata njira, SCI imapereka ngongole pazochitika zonse zomwe zimapangitsa kuti mtima ukhale: kusambira, njinga, kukoka, kuvina, chirichonse. Pitirizani pansi pa 30 kuti mukhale ndi moyo wathanzi komanso wathanzi.
sbpi_desc: Kuthamanga kwa magazi ndi wakupha wakupha. Mankhwala anu a Systolic ndi Diastolic amagwiritsidwa ntchito pa nthawi iliyonse ya zamankhwala yomwe mukuchita. SBPI ikhale pansi pa 30 kuti mukhale ndi mwayi wotsika kuti muvutike ndi zoopsa za moyo monga kupweteka ndi magazi.
sci_desc: Poganizira mawonekedwe anu osokoneza thupi tikupeza zidziwitso za thupi lanu la mtima. Chiwerengero cha SCI ndi chidule cha thanzi lanu la mtima, yesetsani kusunga pansipa 20!

sii_desc: SII ndi kuphatikizapo malemba onse a SaluberMD ndipo ndi galasi lachiopsezo chanu chachikulu cha zachipatala. Ngati muli pansi pa 30 muli pamalo otetezeka!

spo2_desc: SpO2 kapena mlingo wamagazi wa magazi ndi mlingo wa oxygen anu maselo ofiira a magazi. Zomwe zimayendera ndizofika pakati pa 95% ndi 100%, A pansipa-yachibadwa magazi mpweya wotchedwa hypoxemia
sri_desc: Timapenda njira zanu zopuma nthawi iliyonse yachipatala komanso pamene mukugona. Ngati SRI ili m'munsi mwa 30 mwayi wanu kuti muvutike ndi vuto lakupuma ndilochepa.
ssi_desc: Pofufuza kusinthasintha kwa mtima wanu timayesa kuchuluka kwa nkhawa yanu. Kusokonezeka maganizo kumawoneka ngati koopsa kapena kuonjezera chiopsezo cha mikhalidwe monga kunenepa kwambiri, matenda a mtima, matenda a Alzheimer, matenda a shuga, kuvutika maganizo, mavuto a m'mimba, ndi mphumu. Ikani pansi pa 20 kuti mukhale otetezeka!

tipshealt1: Flu shot - Kodi ndiyenera katemera katemera?
tipshealt11: Phindu la mankhwala a statins, kuchepetsa mankhwala a kolesterolini, kupitirira zoopsa
tipshealt12: Akatswiri ofufuza apeza kuti phindu la kuchepetsa LDL cholesterol ndi mankhwala a statin amatha kupeŵa zochitika zazikulu (matenda a mtima, zilonda) ndipo zimaposa kuopsa kwa mankhwalawa.
tipshealt13: Malingana ndi ochita kafukufuku okhawo zochitika zoopsa zomwe zawonetsedwa kuti zimayambitsidwa ndi nthawi yaitali mankhwalawa ndi myopathy (amatanthauza kupweteka kwa minofu kapena kufooka), matenda atsopano a shuga, ndipo, mwinamwake, kupwetekedwa kwa magazi.
tipshealt2: Ngakhale katemera wa chimfine sikuti nthawi zonse amateteza chitetezo, ndibwino kupeza. CDC (Centers for Disease Control and Prevention) imayamikira katemera wa pachakudya kwa aliyense ali ndi zaka 6 kapena kuposa. Katemera ndi wofunika kwambiri kwa anthu omwe ali pachiopsezo chachikulu cha matenda a chimfine, kuphatikizapo
tipshealt5: Ana aang'ono (zaka zoposa 4 ndi zoposa miyezi 6)
tipshealt6: Kuchita masewera olimbitsa thupi kumawonjezera malingaliro ndi luso loganiza
tipshealt7: Kuchita masewera olimbitsa thupi nthawi zonse kungathandize kuti ubongo uzigwira ntchito nthawi yonse ya moyo ndikuchepetsa chiwopsezo cha matenda a maganizo.
tipshealt8: Kafukufuku wambiri wafalitsidwa pa kugwirizana kwachindunji komanso kupindula kwa kuchita masewero olimbitsa thupi komanso ntchito yabwino yodziwa zamaganizo.
tipshealt9: Mphamvuzo zimagwira ntchito pa ubongo komanso mwachindunji kudzera mu zochitika zamagetsi ndi thupi pa thupi.
